{"tid":2442762,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"俄羅斯減慢Twitter網速 疑打壓示威","createTime":"2021-03-11T14:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T14:49:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ff41452d7770d7b691852b2102e2316d76be24ec","tid":2442762,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210311/YBLPVK2FPRDYTCGCISRMGLGUAE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210311%2FYBLPVK2FPRDYTCGCISRMGLGUAE%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHRYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=df146fd8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210311%2FYBLPVK2FPRDYTCGCISRMGLGUAE%2F&h=37e2d170\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210311/YBLPVK2FPRDYTCGCISRMGLGUAE/</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯減慢Twitter網速 疑打壓示威<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8yTA-JKA0YFcT99YBO0VvovWMXA=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GYCPDQFO3ZAUVLOCBXNLM6S4MI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8yTA-JKA0YFcT99YBO0VvovWMXA%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGYCPDQFO3ZAUVLOCBXNLM6S4MI.jpg&h=35372d4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■俄羅斯為遏反對派的聲浪，不惜減慢Twitter速度。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯早前要求社交網Twitter移除「非法呼籲未成年人參與反政府示威」的內容不果，昨日表示正減慢該平台網速。Twitter未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n前日有俄羅斯傳媒引述法庭指，有五個社交平台被控沒有刪除呼籲未成年人參與非法示威的內容，Twitter是其中之一。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或在其他平台實施<br />\n<br />\n國家信息監控局昨日發聲明指，Twitter上有超過3,000則帖文含有非法內容，包含兒童色情、濫藥資訊和煽動未成年人自殺的內容，但未有提及內容與反對派示威有關。當局指「100%流動裝置會受減速影響，非流動裝置則有50%受影響。如Twitter繼續無視法例要求，有關措施將繼續」。有報道引述當局官員指，同樣措施有機會在其他不遵守法例的社交平台上實施。克宮指無意封網，但有關公司必須守法。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯過往在。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/德新社"},{"pid":"b94f64ef00da9f6142dcc1f8280e5969e61a761a","tid":2442762,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}